<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbc7e2db5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s3339"><num value="3339">§ 3339.</num><heading> Limitation on amount of grant</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Grants made under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s3335">section 3335 of this title</ref> for projects in any one State shall not exceed in the aggregate 15 per centum of the aggregate amount of funds authorized to be appropriated pursuant to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s3336/b">section 3336(b) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbc7e2db6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/754/tII/s209">Pub. L. 89–754, title II, § 209</ref>, <date date="1966-11-03">Nov. 3, 1966</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/80/1266">80 Stat. 1266</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
